{"3554770": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Abdomen Expansion", "steam_appid": 3554770, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abdomen Expansion is a minimalist inflation pregnancy clicker game where you click and click until her belly grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554770/extras/a0eb614d50d52c32f730670ee5c8362c.poster.avif?t=1773234632\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554770/extras/a0eb614d50d52c32f730670ee5c8362c.webm?t=1773234632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554770/extras/a0eb614d50d52c32f730670ee5c8362c.mp4?t=1773234632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As I've mentioned, this game is a simple minimalistic clicker game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, that's only on the surface!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game has a &quot;Birth&quot; feature in which you effectively reset the game in exchange for a permanent boost. You have two options on this:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ASSIMILATE:</strong> Each point of this gives a permanent bonus auto clicker.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONSECRATE:</strong> Each point of this gives an increase to all upgrades.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554770/extras/48804465b2e51f8d3d23174626380c7a.poster.avif?t=1773234632\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/